    :topics: Conditionals/Exercises
    :from_source: F

    Write code that will ask the user for a number.  Using ONLY ONE
    if statement, print "This number is even" or "This number is odd".
    Hint: even numbers have a remainder of zero when divided by 2.
    Another hint: use the % operator
    ~~~~